==反响==
《阴间大法师》于1988年4月1日开始在美国院线上映，首周入账803万零897美元，并最终在[[北美地区|北美地区]]获得了7370万7461美元的票房收入，在商业上获得了成功<ref name="BOM"/>，是1988年票房最高的十部电影之一<ref>{{cite news|title=Roger Rabbit' Hops to Box-Office Top; 'Coming to America' Hits 2nd|work=The Los Angeles Times|date=1989-01-05|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1989-01-05/entertainment/ca-271_1_box-office-information|accessdate=2010-10-26|first=Nina J.|last=Easton|archive-date=2012-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120715022513/http://articles.latimes.com/1989-01-05/entertainment/ca-271_1_box-office-information|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=1988&p=.htm | title = 1988 Yearly Box Office Results | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2013-07-02 | archive-date = 2012-02-05 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65DkqvNbC?url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=1988 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的56篇专业影评文章，其中46篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为84%，平均得分7分（满分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beetlejuice/ |title=Beetlejuice |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603081109/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beetlejuice/ |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archivedate=2013-06-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而根据[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的13篇评论文章，其中9篇予以好评，1篇差评，3篇褒贬不一，平均分为67（满分100）<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/beetle-juice| title = Beetlejuice (1988): Reviews| work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]| accessdate = 2013-07-02| archive-date = 2013-01-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130117054702/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/beetle-juice| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

{{link-en|宝琳·卡尔|Pauline Kael}}称本片是一部“喜剧经典”<ref name="Batman" />{{rp|68-69}}，《芝加哥读者》的乔纳森·罗森堡也给予非常高的评价，他觉得本片所承载的独创性和创造力都是别的电影中所不具备的<ref>{{cite news | author = Jonathan Rosenbaum | url = http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/beetlejuice/Film?oid=1916802 | title = Beetlejuice | work = Chicago Reader | date = 1988-04-01 | accessdate = 2013-07-02 | archive-date = 2013-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022103447/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/beetlejuice/Film?oid=1916802 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的文森特·坎拜（{{lang|en|Vincent Canby}}）称其为“我们时代的一场闹剧”，并希望基顿的出场时间能够再多一点<ref>{{cite news | author = Vincent Canby | title = ''Beetle Juice'' is Pap For The Eyes | work = The New York Times | date = 1988-05-08 | accessdate = 2008-04-04}}</ref>。玛丽安·约翰森（{{lang|en|MaryAnn Johanson}}）对片中的演员表现、艺术指导和笑话留下了深刻的印象<ref>{{cite news|author=MaryAnn Johanson |url=http://www.flickfilosopher.com/2003/10/evil-dead-ii-army-of-darkness-young-frankenstein-little-shop-of-horrors-and-beetlejuice-review.html |title=''Evil Dead II'', ''Army of Darkness'', ''Young Frankenstein'', ''Little Shop of Horrors'', and ''Beetle Juice'' (review) |work=Flick Filosopher |date=2003-10-31 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080309113603/http://www.flickfilosopher.com/blog/2003/10/evil_dead_ii_army_of_darkness.html |archivedate=2008-03-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的德森·汤姆森（{{lang|en|Desson Thomson}}）觉得《阴间大法师》“在喜剧、恐怖和离奇之间有着完美的平衡<ref>{{cite news | author = Desson Howe | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/beetlejuicepghowe_a0b155.htm | title = Beetle Juice | work = Washington Post | date = 1988-04-01 | accessdate = 2008-04-04 | archive-date = 2008-11-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081119032812/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/beetlejuicepghowe_a0b155.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

不过，《纽约时报》的简妮特·玛丝琳（{{lang|en|Janet Maslin}}）给予电影负面评价，认为该片“把任何事情都用来做效果，只是偶然才会有一些稍微搞笑的内容。”而且“也就只有一颗被缩小的头那么好笑而已”<ref>{{cite news| author = Janet Maslin | title = Beetlejuice (1988) | work = The New York Times | date = 1988-03-08 | accessdate = 2010-06-13}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]给予影片两星的评价（最高四星），认为要是剧情中能用一些闪回镜头介绍一下麦特兰夫妇的甜蜜感情，那这部电影还会更有意思一点。对于基顿的角色，艾伯特称其“在几磅重的妆后面根本没法认出来”，并表示“他的镜头看起来与其它部分很不搭”<ref>{{cite news| author = Roger Ebert| url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/beetlejuice-1988| title = Beetlejuice| work = Chicago Sun-Times| date = 1988-03-30| accessdate = 2013-07-02| archive-date = 2013-07-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130723180307/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/beetlejuice-1988| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

