影片还获得了[[土星奖|土星奖]]{{link-en|土星奖最佳恐怖電影|Saturn Award for Best Horror Film|最佳恐怖片}}和{{link-en|土星奖最佳化妆|Saturn Award for Best Make-up|最佳化妆}}奖，西尔维娅·西德尼也因出演朱诺一角赢得了[[土星獎最佳電影女配角|最佳女配角奖]]，此外还有最佳{{link-en|土星奖最佳导演|Saturn Award for Best Director|最佳导演}}、{{link-en|土星奖最佳编剧|Saturn Award for Best Writing|编剧}}、[[土星獎最佳電影男配角|男配角]]、{{link-en|土星奖最佳音乐|Saturn Award for Best Music|最佳音乐}}和{{link-en|土星奖最佳特技效果|Saturn Award for Best Special Effects|最佳特技效果}}5项提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saturnawards.org/past.html#film |title=Past Saturn Awards |publisher=Saturn Awards |accessdate=2010-06-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202111125/http://www.saturnawards.org/past.html |archivedate=2014-02-02 }}</ref>。《阴间大法师》获得了[[雨果奖|雨果奖]]{{link-en|雨果奖最佳戏剧表现|Hugo Award for Best Dramatic Presentation|最佳戏剧表现奖}}提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1989-hugo-awards/ |title=1989 Hugo Awards |publisher=The Hugo Awards |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612033831/http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1989-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2010-06-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2000年，[[美国影艺协会|美国影艺协会]]评选[[AFI百年电影史百大喜剧电影|AFI百年电影史百大喜剧电影]]，《阴间大法师》名列第88位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.afi.com/100years/laughs.aspx |title=AFI's 100 YEARS...100 LAUGHS |work=American Film Institute |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514072559/http://www.afi.com/100Years/laughs.aspx |archivedate=2013-05-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

