2011年9月，华纳兄弟公司请来[[赛斯·格雷厄姆-史密斯|赛斯·格雷厄姆-史密斯]]担任《阴间大法师》的编剧和制片人，他曾与波顿在《[[黑暗阴影|黑暗阴影]]》和《[[吸血鬼猎人林肯_(电影)|吸血鬼猎人林肯]]》中合作过<ref>{{cite news | author = Mike Fleming | title = KatzSmith Duo Makes First-Look Warner Bros Deal; Will Bring ‘Beetlejuice’ Back From Dead | work = Deadline.com | url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/09/katzsmith-duo-makes-first-look-warner-bros-deal-will-bring-beetlejuice-back-from-dead/ | date = 2011-09-06 | accessdate = 2013-07-02 | archive-date = 2013-07-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130702061229/http://www.deadline.com/2011/09/katzsmith-duo-makes-first-look-warner-bros-deal-will-bring-beetlejuice-back-from-dead/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。格雷厄姆-史密斯加入这个项目是为了创作“一个真的值得我们开拍的故事，而不只是为了赚钞票，也不只是非要强拍出一部重拍片或是重启之作”。他还坚决要求让基顿继续出演其原本的角色，华纳兄弟不得另请高明。波顿和基顿还没有正式签约，但表示要是剧本够好他们都愿意回归<ref>{{cite news|author=John Ary |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/55824 |title=John Ary With A Brief Snippet Of Info Re: Beetlejuice 2 Via Writer Seth Grahame-Smith!! |work=Ain't It Cool News |date=2012-05-17 |accessdate=2013-07-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522005333/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/55824 |archivedate=2012-05-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。波顿与格雷厄姆-史密斯曾于2012年2月见面，“我们聊了两个小时，谈到了有关大片的事情。这对华纳兄弟或是蒂姆来说都是优先考虑的。（迈克尔）想拍这部电影已经想了20年了，他会向任何愿意倾听的人诉说。”<ref>{{cite news | author = Ryan Turek | url = http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/165575-michael-keaton-meets-about-beetlejuice-2-seth-grahame-smith-offers-update | title = Michael Keaton Meets About Beetlejuice 2, Seth Grahame-Smith Offers Update | work = Crave Online | publisher = ShockTilYouDrop.com | date = 2012-02-11 | accessdate = 2013-07-02 | archive-date = 2013-06-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130613204312/http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/165575-michael-keaton-meets-about-beetlejuice-2-seth-grahame-smith-offers-update | dead-url = no }}</ref>这个故事将与1988年的电影相隔的时间同步，“这会是一部真正的26或27年后的续集。对于阴间大法师来说，时间没有任何意义，但对于外面的世界那可就完全不同了。”<ref name=collider/>

2013年10月，據報導，波頓正在為導演續集的事宜與華納兄弟討論<ref>{{cite web|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|url=https://www.thewrap.com/tim-burton-talks-direct-michael-keaton-beetlejuice-2-warner-bros/|title=Tim Burton in Talks to Direct Michael Keaton in ‘Beetlejuice 2’ for Warner Bros.|website=TheWrap|date=2013-10-21|accessdate=2019-09-13|archive-date=2019-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014215614/https://www.thewrap.com/tim-burton-talks-direct-michael-keaton-beetlejuice-2-warner-bros/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年11月，瑞德暗示她有可能會回歸續集：「我可以說是應該要保密的，但這真的有可能會成真。27年過去了。我不得不說，我好愛麗迪亞·迪茲。對我而言，她是如此的重要。我真的對她27年後會做什麼很感興趣。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Romano|first=Andrew|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/11/18/exclusive-winona-ryder-on-beetlejuice-2-looks-like-it-s-happening-with-burton-keaton-and-ryder.html|title=Winona Ryder on‘Beetlejuice 2': 'Might Be Happening’ With Burton, Keaton, and Ryder|website=[[The_Daily_Beast|The Daily Beast]]|date=2013-11-18|accessdate=2013-11-27|archive-date=2013-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131126055912/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/11/18/exclusive-winona-ryder-on-beetlejuice-2-looks-like-it-s-happening-with-burton-keaton-and-ryder.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>瑞德也表明，只有在波頓和基頓回歸的前提下，她才會考慮出演續集。2014年12月，波頓表示，「（-{zh-cn:阴间大法师;zh-tw:甲蟲汁大師;}-）是我很喜歡的一個角色，而且我也很懷念和與演員麥可（·基頓）的合作時光。-{zh-cn:阴间大法师;zh-tw:甲蟲汁大師;}-只有一個。我們正在編寫一份劇本，我想這回我們可能比以往都更接近成功了，而且我很樂意與他再一次合作。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Douglas|first=Edward|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/392099-exclusive-tim-burton-thinks-theyre-closer-than-ever-to-beetlejuice-sequel|title=Exclusive: Tim Burton Thinks Beetlejuice 2 is Closer Than Ever|date=2014-12-14|website=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]]|publisher=[[CraveOnline|CraveOnline]]|accessdate=2015-05-20|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510223957/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/392099-exclusive-tim-burton-thinks-theyre-closer-than-ever-to-beetlejuice-sequel|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年1月，編劇格雷厄姆-史密斯告訴《[[娱乐周刊|娛樂週刊]]》，續集的劇本已經完工，他和波頓打算在年底前就開拍，而且基頓和瑞德都會回歸<ref>{{cite web|last=Breznican|first=Anthony|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/01/16/beetlejuice-2-something-wicked-gremlins-seth-grahame-smith/3|title='Beetlejuice' 2, 'Something Wicked,' 'Gremlins,' vampires galore: Seth Grahame-Smith's 2015 to-do list|website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2015-01-16|accessdate=2015-08-12|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924143556/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/01/16/beetlejuice-2-something-wicked-gremlins-seth-grahame-smith/3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年8月，在脫口秀《[[塞斯·梅耶斯深夜秀|塞斯·梅耶斯深夜秀]]》上，瑞德證實自己將出演續集<ref>{{cite magazine|title='Beetlejuice 2' Is Really Happening, Says Winona Ryder|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/news/beetlejuice-2-sequel-winona-ryder-tim-burton-michael-keaton-1201567607/|accessdate=2015-09-13|first=Mannie|last=Holmes|magazine=Variety|date=2015-08-11|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907013642/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/beetlejuice-2-sequel-winona-ryder-tim-burton-michael-keaton-1201567607/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年5月，波頓表示：「如果續集的元素正確的話，未來大家一定看得到，只是現在還沒有具體成品問世而已。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|url=http://collider.com/beetlejuice-2-update-tim-burton/|title=Beetlejuice 2: Tim Burton Gives Update on Sequel|website=Collider|date=2016-05-10|accessdate=2016-11-11|archive-date=2016-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116103357/http://collider.com/beetlejuice-2-update-tim-burton|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年10月，麥克·弗卡迪諾維區（Mike Vukadinovich）受聘重寫劇本<ref>{{cite news|last=Busch|first=Anita|url=https://deadline.com/2017/10/beetlejuice-2-new-writer-mike-vukadinovich-warner-bros-tim-burton-1202184970/|title=‘Beetlejuice 2’ Pushes Forward With New Writer At Warner Bros.|website=Deadline.com|date=2017-10-12|accessdate=2019-04-09|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407065935/https://deadline.com/2017/10/beetlejuice-2-new-writer-mike-vukadinovich-warner-bros-tim-burton-1202184970/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年4月，華納兄弟宣布，《阴间大法师》的續集已被擱置<ref>{{cite news|last=Alexander|first=Bryan|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2019/04/02/beetlejuice-sequel-tim-burton-michael-keaton/3337292002/|title=Tim Burton's 'Beetlejuice' sequel is stuck in the afterlife waiting room|website=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|date=2019-04-02|accessdate=2019-04-09|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407021141/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2019/04/02/beetlejuice-sequel-tim-burton-michael-keaton/3337292002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

